{
  "text": "In Fig.4 the motion is along the x-axis. In the limiting case of a point-like particle, one obtains only a double cone. In 1982, therefore, it was predicted [CITATION_1] that the simplest Superluminal object appears (not as a particle, but as a field or rather) as a wave:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "117745432"
